      *                  *  - Corpo  effettivo                         *
      *                  *  - Bottom effettivo                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-for-eft-sel        to   w-for-tcb-sel          .
           add       w-for-efc-sel        to   w-for-tcb-sel          .
           add       w-for-efb-sel        to   w-for-tcb-sel          .
