      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-lin-stp-bln        from w-sbc-xyz-xln          .
       emi-seq-lin-310.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuale griglia                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da generare                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su numero linea                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin                <    06
                     go to emi-seq-lin-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su contenuto linea                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lin-stp-cnt        =    spaces
                     go to emi-seq-lin-900.
